| ZPIQSMFU_CALC | Calculate and publish final grades | Course code → Students → Attendance (check) → Grade Supervisor (check) → Final Result → select all → calculator → Accord → Block → Save |
| ZPIQSTFU | Update single student grade/attendance | Student number → AY + period → double-click course → adjust → Grade Supervisor row → Final Result → calculator → Accord → Block → Save |
| ZPIQ_MASS_EXAM | Register resit students | AY = FIRST year of AY. Period = period course took place (NOT resit period). Enter course code → multiple selection → paste student numbers → upload from clipboard → Execute → untick Test → Execute → Save |

